title: Mera Farz
subTitle: Aalwar, a temple priest, leads a peaceful life until his mother and sister are murdered. In an attempt to take revenge, he adopts various disguises to teach a lesson to the perpetrators.

title: Vijayadasami
subTitle: Disowned by his family, a young man relocates to the city and falls in love with the daughter of a rich businessman. Eventually, he decides to return to his village and challenge his evil brothers.

title: Friday The 13th
subTitle: The 13th page of a mysterious book harbours evil. It gives rise to a series of devastating events as people who read it, get possessed by demonic spirits.

title: Ram Ki Jung
subTitle: Ram does not believe in everlasting love and this ideology does not go down well with Jaanu. When Abhishek, a police officer, asks him the reason, he tells him about Rooba, his former lover.

title: Daring Gundaraaj
subTitle: Jagan falls for Sunanda, who happens to be the daughter of his father's business rival. Further hilarity ensues when the two tycoons unknowingly broker a match between their love-struck children.

title: Angel
subTitle: Nani discovers a rare antique idol from the excavation site at Amaravati. He wants to sell it and keep the money for himself, but before he can do that, the idol goes missing.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi 2
subTitle: Balu grows up without the love of a family due to his parents' untimely death. Later, he decides to establish a firm to help people like himself receive the affection they missed out on.

title: Yudh Ek Jung
subTitle: Chandu, a supermarket employee, encounters trouble when he decides to help Indu, an aspiring actress, and gets embroiled in a murder case.

title: Sita Ram
subTitle: Ram, a young boy, lives in a monastery waiting for Sita to return and take care of him. However, Sita returns, years later, but with an ulterior motive.

title: DD Returns
subTitle: An event manager and his friends hide the money they stole in a haunted bungalow to evade the police but when they go back to retrieve it, the ghosts force them to play a dangerous game.

title: Loafer
subTitle: Seenu, a man who wants to go to Dubai, meets and falls in love with Madhumati. When he discovers that a dreaded don has killed his friend and Madhumati's brother, he sets out to exact revenge.

title: Bunglow No 17
subTitle: Gautham and Deeksha, along with their daughter, move into an isolated bungalow gifted to them by Gautham's father. Soon, they start experiencing paranormal activities around the house.

title: Mahabali Bal Ganesh VI
subTitle: Top, Dhoti and Suitboot land on Kailash Parbat where they meet Nandi and Mooshak Raj. There, they come across stories about Bal Ganesh, who fights to rid the world of demons.

title: Auzaar
subTitle: Suraj, a police officer, is assigned to arrest his friend Yash, whose father runs an illegal business. He must now persuade his friend to make his father change his ways to avoid the consequences.

title: Jajantaram Mamantaram
subTitle: Aditya finds himself on an island after surviving a shipwreck. Here, he realises he is a giant amongst its inhabitants, who think he going to save them from a terrifying demon.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Bharaate
subTitle: Jagan, a local travel guide, falls in love with Radha, a tourist who visits his city. Though she leaves without saying goodbye, fate conspires to being them together again.

title: Kee
subTitle: Siddharth, a hacker who is blessed with a happy family, falls in love with a girl. However, his life changes drastically when he becomes a victim of cyberbullying that leads him to another hacker.

title: Satyabhama
subTitle: ACP Satyabhama embarks on an investigation into a missing person case, which leads her to uncover dark secrets hidden within the town. However, as she delves deeper, her past begins to haunt her.

title: Buddy
subTitle: A terrible accident leaves Pallavi in a coma while her soul possesses the body of a teddy bear. With her organs in danger of being traded, she enlists the help of a pilot, Aditya.

title: Ragada
subTitle: Satya, a money-minded man, arrives in Hyderabad and starts working for a gangster, GK. However, he soon becomes the target of another gangster, Peddanna.

title: Meri Ladaai
subTitle: An ambitious real estate agent falls in love with the sister of a powerful business tycoon. However, the girl's brother resents their relationship and tries to separate the lovers.

title: Meri Ladaai
subTitle: An ambitious real estate agent falls in love with the sister of a powerful business tycoon. However, the girl's brother resents their relationship and tries to separate the lovers.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: Vijay, a dedicated police officer, is shattered to discover his brother Aftab is a ruthless criminal. Torn between duty and love, Vijay embarks on a relentless quest to bring him to justice.

title: Khal-Naaikaa
subTitle: A pregnant woman's life turns into a nightmare after her husband commits suicide and she loses her unborn child. Embittered, the woman embarks on a quest for revenge.

title: Athiratha
subTitle: Following a family legacy, a youngster ventures into journalism and investigates a scandal involving a powerful politician. However, his life moves downhill after he is arrested under a false charge.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Manjulika Returns 2
subTitle: Four strangers across different walks of life serendipitously meet at a haunted graveyard. However, luck turns to misery when an insidious force awakens.

title: Jaguar
subTitle: Krishna, an orphan medical student, lives a seemingly ordinary life. However, unbeknownst to people, he is a vigilante named Jaguar who pursues a certain group of people in order to kill them.

title: MCA: Middle Class Abbayi
subTitle: Nani, a middle-class boy with an eidetic memory, helps save his sister-in-law from a goon. Meanwhile, he also tries to convince his girlfriend's father to marry her off to him.

title: Daaku Maharaaj
subTitle: A brave thief fights to survive and claim his territory. However, he battles powerful enemies, aiming to become a leader without a real kingdom.

title: Power Unlimited
subTitle: The home minister asks Tirupathi to impersonate the deceased ACP Baldev, his lookalike, to catch Ganguly, a dreaded gangster. After taking over his new role, he finds many startling revelations.
